com.juraj.hdbs.querying.language

Interface GlobalSQLListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GlobalSQLBaseListener

    public interface GlobalSQLListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by GlobalSQLParser.
